ActCustoms Tariff
SubjectCPFTA Tariff Preference Regulations
PrecisCanada-Peru Free Trade Agreement Tariff Preference Regulations (CPFTA) allow eligible goods that are not shipped directly between Peru and Canada to retain their eligibility for preferential tariff rates provided that they remain under customs control in third countries.
